Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the design and development of a semi-autonomous lawn mowing system from a robotics perspective.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper discusses the problem from a systems engineering perspective and proposes a general system architecture.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the system is semi-autonomous and likely involves some level of AI for decision-making.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the system likely involves software development for control and decision-making.
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is less likely but still possible as the system may involve multiple agents (e.g. sensors, actuators) working together.
